{"tid":1646043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立法會財委會擬準備動議黑警加薪","createTime":"2019-10-11T06:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T13:47:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b4df89f9ae150557d50de5d7a9f9eea220dacd16","tid":1646043,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485529-20191011.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485529-20191011.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwchAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=c119a641\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485529-20191011.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=be883f59\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485529-20191011.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1485529_1_L_20191011122947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1485529_1_L_20191011122947.jpg&h=a06325bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會大樓復修後，今日早上舉行首次財委會會議，選舉正、副主席，由於民主派提名多人角逐，最終出現有23名主席候選人，當中只有角逐連任的陳健波屬建制派。會議舉行兩個多小時，仍未能選出主席。<br />\n<br />\n民主派議員質疑，陳健波對公務員加薪撥款申請中，是否抽起警員加薪部分有預設立場。建制派議員就批評，民主派議員拖延會議，浪費時間。"},{"pid":"c56c463e2b7c44b0f951cd223c83e556028a4689","tid":1646043,"uid":226271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:41:45.000Z","msg":"仲加？傻撚咗？佢個腦裝屎？"},{"pid":"6b5a71274f399bf868917b263c9018b151076ded","tid":1646043,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c56c463e2b7c44b0f951cd223c83e556028a4689","tid":1646043,"uid":226271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:41:45.000Z","msg":"仲加？傻撚咗？佢個腦裝屎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T06:43:07.000Z","msg":"成功保護權貴<br />\n<br />\n權貴當然會加佢地薪"},{"pid":"43f07d43438e465353f4ae83336213b878032811","ti